column5: My Wife got her Tattoo last Saturday & We got the word Andy could fit My Daughter & I in today so off to Thrive Studios in Cambridge for our tattoo's, I was going to get 2 done today but the Largemouth Bass wasn't painted yet & so we put it off until the next time I can get down, SBK
Thats awesome SBK. I love tattoos.
Very nice!!! I love your choice of nail polish BTW   JK  Paul
she's brave getting that one on top of her foot.  bet that hurt a bunch.
very beautiful tattoo....On the first picture, when she stands up from a seat, will the fish swing its tail  ?
